{"id":148466,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/終結「無聊」議題-歐巴馬秀出生證明-聯合新聞網/","date":"2011-04-28T21:30:52Z","modified":"2011-04-28T21:43:29Z","title":"終結「無聊」議題 歐巴馬秀出生證明","content":"<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"7\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"80\"><a href=\"http://news.google.com/news/url?sa=t&#038;fd=R&#038;usg=AFQjCNE9Ejzet55cP5tYpYUKZDCYggXtVQ&#038;url=http://udn.com/NEWS/WORLD/WOR6/6302882.shtml\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"1\" height=\"50\" src=\"http://nt0.ggpht.com/news/tbn/tKR4guERFpc7IM/0.jpg\" width=\"80\" /><br />聯合新聞網</a></td>\n<td valign=\"top\"></p>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://news.google.com/news/url?sa=t&#038;fd=R&#038;usg=AFQjCNE9Ejzet55cP5tYpYUKZDCYggXtVQ&#038;url=http://udn.com/NEWS/WORLD/WOR6/6302882.shtml\"><b>終結「無聊」議題 歐巴馬秀出生證明</b></a><br /><b>聯合新聞網</b><br />為了讓自己出生地的爭議畫下句點，美國總統歐巴馬指示白宮向夏威夷政府調出當年出生證明的完整版，27日公諸於世。歐巴馬甚至臨時出現在白宮簡報室，表示他決定公布出生證明，以終結關於此事的「無聊」把戲。 歐巴馬表示：「如果我們因為枝節問題和雜耍的吆喝就分心，我們 <b>&#8230;</b><br /><a href=\"http://news.google.com/news/url?sa=t&#038;fd=R&#038;usg=AFQjCNF4qXpxkMVe6UZLL5w9vpuTFtGjaA&#038;url=http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2011/new/apr/28/today-int7.htm\">出生地爭議 歐巴馬澄清</a>自由時報<br /><a href=\"http://news.google.com/news/url?sa=t&#038;fd=R&#038;usg=AFQjCNGiLQyprOPQefJRhMLShIJmDbsnlQ&#038;url=http://www.singpao.com/NewsArticle.aspx?NewsID%3D166191%26Lang%3Dtc\">證據確鑿奧巴馬夏威夷出生</a>成報<br /><a href=\"http://news.google.com/news/url?sa=t&#038;fd=R&#038;usg=AFQjCNFRgGqCnOM5Aoo3GbUEw8BnTzYxRw&#038;url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2011/04/110427_obama_birthcertificat.shtml\">奧巴馬公開出生證澄清出生地傳言</a>BBC中文網<br /><a href=\"http://news.google.com/news/url?sa=t&#038;fd=R&#038;usg=AFQjCNEUj9QFAqfvAFKmoxtBq-VBPo6nUQ&#038;url=http://news.rti.org.tw/index_newsContent.aspx?nid%3D293769%26id%3D2%26id2%3D2\">中央廣播電台</a> &#8211;<a href=\"http://news.google.com/news/url?sa=t&#038;fd=R&#038;usg=AFQjCNEhwDTySFzZruqO98U3pE1gPjQ8iQ&#038;url=http://www